Title: Odyssey OCN: Future of Decentralized Sharing Economy
Body: Odyssey (OCN) Successfully Integrates Obike Modernizing Sharing Economy Payments  Singapore blockchain-based start-up Odyssey is a digital asset mobile payment solution offering an integrated cryptocurrency wallet. The tech startup has recently announced its strategic partnership with the oBike Global Bike Sharing Platform. The native OCN token will be the very first digital integrated token in the decentralized sharing economy. A solid move by Odyssey, now able to enhance the international payments of circa 10 million oBike users, just using the Odyssey Wallet and usage of the OCN token.  Singapore founded blockchain startup, has just announced the completion of its digital asset mobile solution. This platform will go hand in hand with bike-sharing provider oBike.
